<item>
            <title>[SUREFIRE-973] add properties to classpathDependencyExcludes and additionalClasspathElements parameters</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-973</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;currently classpathDependencyExcludes and additionalClasspathElements parameters don&apos;t have properties defined to declare on cmd line. The attached patch includes them.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I would like to use these properties in Netbeans. With multiple projects enabling Compile on Save feature, I would need these properties to replace outside project&apos;s jar artifacts from local repository with their project&apos;s output directory dynamically.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
